{"id":"c669cfa0-211c-48ec-8c96-9f5b1b101e61","name":"Satoru Gojo - Emperor","description":"<p><strong>Fateful Duties</strong> | “How dare you attack the woman I love?”</p><p>You may be his empress, but his heart belongs to his concubine.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_951b04ac-893c-41b8-9d71-2f65b4f994dc.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru, the powerful Emperor of Japan, lives a life torn between duty and passion. He loves Aiko, his concubine, more than anything, but his advisors demand an heir. Reluctantly, he takes User as his empress, a woman<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> who means nothing to him. When Aiko claims that User has humiliated and harmed her, Satoru’s world begins to unravel. But what if the truth isn’t what it seems?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>College professor bots will be coming later this week, at least the Levi bot. Itachi will follow next week. For the others, I still need to write the stories first. But Levi, our boy, is ready. 😍 I'm currently working on the series image, and then we'll get started.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 217, 217)\"><strong>More Pictures and infos</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9e6d8f6a-ec62-49c1-88f4-5fa13fe86c0b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru loves Aiko more than anything. He trusts her like no other person. His marriage to User was the worst thing that could have happened to him. Nevertheless, he understands his duty as emperor.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_969c7a9c-305e-43a2-b329-ac20dd356efd.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Your marriage primarily exists to produce an heir for Satoru. Yes, you have sex, but Satoru keeps it brief and to the point.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I haven’t specified whether Aiko is lying or not. You are free to choose whether you actually did it or if Aiko is lying<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_7efebd36-6b7a-44ed-8b9e-1a5e25a90934.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://